LAST-MODIFIED:20260613T182800Z
DTSTART:20260608T203000Z
DTEND:20260608T223000Z
SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 34 - The Pump Can't Hurt Me
 Anymore... Right?
DESCRIPTION:Back on the construction site and ready to continue building -
 assuming the concrete pump doesn't have other plans. Surely we've won this
 battle by now... right? Construction Simulator is back - bigger and better
 than ever! Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them brand new to
 the franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge maps - on
 your own or with your friends!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IGqDt6YuMPY
CATEGORIES:Construction Simulator
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23552211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260519T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260613T182800Z
DTSTART:20260609T203000Z
DTEND:20260609T223000Z
SUMMARY:Dune: Awakening | Ep. 24 - Back on Arrakis, Now Where Did I Park
 My Ornithopter?
DESCRIPTION:We're heading back to Arrakis for more survival, exploration,
 and sand-related problems. The only challenge now is remembering where I
 left my transport. Rise from survival to greatness and challenge the power
 of an Imperium in Dune: Awakening, a brand-new open world survival and
 crafting game. Alone or together with others, you must survive the
 sandworm, build a home, craft your ornithopter, and unravel the story of
 the missing Fremen.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kuSZB3Hiq7k
CATEGORIES:Dune: Awakening
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23562211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260520T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260613T182800Z
DTSTART:20260610T203000Z
DTEND:20260610T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite III | Ep. 3 - Halfaya Pass
DESCRIPTION:The desert campaign continues with long-range precision,
 stealth tactics, and those moments where everything depends on a single
 shot. Sniper Elite 3 is a tactical third-person shooter that combines
 stealth, gameplay choice and genre-defining ballistics with huge, open
 levels and the exotic terrain of World War 2 North Africa.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzOJvWYJm7
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite III
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23572211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260521T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260613T182800Z
DTSTART:20260611T203000Z
DTEND:20260611T223000Z
SUMMARY:I Am Fish | Ep. 4 - I Believe I Can Swim... Wait, Why Am I Flying?
DESCRIPTION:Physics, logic, and common sense take the evening off. Join me
 as we attempt to guide our aquatic friend through another series of
 increasingly questionable situations. I Am Fish is a charming,
 physics-based adventure starring four intrepid fish friends, forcibly
 separated from their home in a pet shop fish tank. Swim, fly, roll and
 chomp your way to the open ocean in a bid for freedom and to re-unite once
 again.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=deG1mXMXfUg
CATEGORIES:I Am Fish
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
