SUMMARY:I Am Fish | Ep. 5 - Today's Mood: Piranha With a Touch of
 Pufferfish Panic
DESCRIPTION:More physics-based chaos awaits! Join me as we attempt to
 navigate increasingly ridiculous situations while trying to keep our fishy
 friends alive. I Am Fish is a charming, physics-based adventure starring
 four intrepid fish friends, forcibly separated from their home in a pet
 shop fish tank. Swim, fly, roll and chomp your way to the open ocean in a
 bid for freedom and to re-unite once again.
